[ Crewmen Groaning ]

01:00.107 --> 01:03.372
- [ Men Cheering ]
- [ Chuckles ]

01:03.443 --> 01:06.674
You boys eat your vegetables
or I'll do the same to you.

01:06.713 --> 01:09.147
